*Kilometara* od njega je bio veliki zid (He was a great wall of kilometers away from him).
*Prešla je preko *kilometara* zemlje (She crossed over kilometers of land).
*Njegova kuća je bila udaljena samo nekoliko *kilometara* (His house was only a few kilometers away).
*U dve *kilometra* od mosta je bilo pravo uzbuđenje (Two kilometers from the bridge was real excitement).
*Putovanje od *kilometra* trajalo je duže nego što je očekivao (The journey of kilometers took longer than he expected).